# Keep the Docker build context lean (used by the root-context backend image).
**/node_modules/
**/.git/
**/.turbo/
**/dist/
**/build/
**/coverage/
**/.pytest_cache/
**/.ruff_cache/
**/.local_vector_store/

# React Native native projects are never needed in a server image.
apps/mobile/android/
apps/mobile/ios/

# Never ship secrets or the knowledge corpus.
**/.env
**/.env.*
!**/.env.example
**/*ServiceAccountKey*.json
services/chatbot/data/*
!services/chatbot/data/.gitkeep
!services/chatbot/data/SOURCES.md

# Cruft
**/.DS_Store
*.log
